  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The soap on a rope behavioral trial is a school-randomized trial to determine if a disruptive
      cue (the soap on a rope hall pass) can influence hand washing behavior for students in
      Namwala District, Zambia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
