  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in hand washing behavior</measure>
    <time_frame>Handwashing behavior will be monitored at three time points: baseline, 3 weeks following the intervention, and 8 weeks following the intervention.</time_frame>
    <description>Students exiting the latrine will be monitored to determine if they wash their hands using soap and water.</description>
